solving crimes, but this case felt different.

4
00:00:14.290 --> 00:00:18.540 
It all started when he received a call
about a missing person named Sonia.

5
00:00:18.770 --> 00:00:22.600 
She was last seen at a local cafe, and
her family was worried.

6
00:00:22.870 --> 00:00:26.000 
Tom arrived at the cafe and began to ask questions.

7
00:00:26.310 --> 00:00:28.920 
The waitress, a friendly woman named

8
