Laura, told him that Sonia had been
acting strangely before her disappearance.

9
00:00:33.990 --> 00:00:38.000 
She seemed scared, Laura said, like she
was hiding something.

10
00:00:38.310 --> 00:00:42.560 
As Tom dug deeper, he discovered that
Sonia had been involved in a secret

11
00:00:42.570 --> 00:00:43.680 
project at her job.

12
00:00:43.830 --> 00:00:45.640 
She worked for a company developing

13
00:00:45.650 --> 00:00:50.240 
