be connected to some dangerous activities.

14
00:00:50.570 --> 00:00:53.740 
Tom thought about how this could be
related to her disappearance.

15
00:00:54.210 --> 00:00:59.480 
One night, while reviewing his notes, Tom
received an anonymous message on his phone.

16
00:00:59.750 --> 00:01:02.040 
It read, Meet me at the park at midnight.

17
00:01:02.050 --> 00:01:04.040 
I have information about Sonia.

18
00:01:04.710 --> 00:01:07.300 
Tom felt a mix of excitement and fear.

19
00:01:07.590 --> 00:01:08.340 
Who could it be?

20
00:01:08.570 --> 00:01:10.540 
He decided to go, hoping for answers.

21
00:01:10.890 --> 00:01:13.540 
At the park, he met a man named Benny,

22
00:01:13.770 --> 00:01:15.640 
who claimed to know Sonia's whereabouts.

23
00:01:16.150 --> 00:01:18.220 
She's in trouble, Benny said urgently.

24
00:01:18.610 --> 00:01:22.540 
The company is involved in illegal
activities, and Sonia found out.

25
00:01:22.850 --> 00:01:25.280 
Tom felt a chill run down his spine.

26
00:01:25.530 --> 00:01:27.300 
This was bigger than he had imagined.

27
00:01:27.310 --> 00:01:30.400 
Suddenly, Benny revealed that he had evidence.

28
00:01:30.670 --> 00:01:33.120 
A video showing Sonia confronting her

29
00:01:33.130 --> 00:01:35.640 
boss about the unethical practices at the company.

30
00:01:35.810 --> 00:01:37.660 
But just as he was about to share it,

31
00:01:37.850 --> 00:01:39.680 
they heard footsteps approaching.

32
00:01:40.050 --> 00:01:41.020 
It was the police.

33
00:01:41.330 --> 00:01:45.980 
Benny panicked and ran away, leaving Tom
with more questions than answers.

34
00:01:46.470 --> 00:01:49.980 
In the end, Tom decided to confront
Sonia's boss directly.

35
00:01:50.370 --> 00:01:53.600 
He gathered enough evidence and presented
it to the authorities.

36
00:01:53.610 --> 00:01:57.000 
With their help, they found Sonia safe
but shaken.

37
00:01:57.250 --> 00:02:01.140 
She explained that she had gone into
hiding after discovering the truth about

38
00:02:01.150 --> 00:02:01.600 
her company.

39
